    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：AuthVault自环，然后到PaymentGateway，再回连到AuthVault。接下来呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
