    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这里有个关键循环——每次提交交易时，PaymentGateway要把请求丢进TransactionQueue排队处理。这个循环逻辑需要框起来强调。",
      "elements_involved": [
